            "title": "AI獨角獸企業MiniMax及智譜據悉快將啟動香港IPO",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"AI獨角獸企業MiniMax及智譜據悉快將啟動香港IPO\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/MbTM.SN2CYITD.vuNo7mqg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/b1c2d3f0-9369-11f0-be97-94bd773c1563\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">AI獨角獸企業MiniMax及智譜據悉快將啟動香港IPO</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
