        {
            "title": "中央經濟工作會議今昔對比：房地產優先級滑至末尾；新提靈活降準降息",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中共中央經濟工作會議周三至周四在北京舉行。對比2025年與2024年的會後通稿發現，決策層對來年重點任務的表述排序出現顯著變化，其中重點領域風險化解和穩定房地產市場從第五位改為最後提及。此外，去年的「適時降準降息」也變成了「靈活高效運用降準降息等多種政策工具」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以下為2025年與2024年的通稿要點比較：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E4%BB%8A%E6%98%94%E5%B0%8D%E6%AF%94-%E6%88%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E5%84%AA%E5%85%88%E7%B4%9A%E6%BB%91%E8%87%B3%E6%9C%AB%E5%B0%BE-%E6%96%B0%E6%8F%90%E9%9D%88%E6%B4%BB%E9%99%8D%E6%BA%96%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF-213645801.html",
